OL,3,CMan charged over arson attack on
OL,4,Cleisure centre during riots
OL,6,FA man has been charged to court over
OL,7,Fan arson attack at a Co Antrim leisure
OL,8,Fcentre during rioting in the summer.
OL,10,FRace-related anti-immigration violence
OL,11,Fflared in Ballymena in June before
OL,12,Fspreading to other parts of Northern
OL,13,FIreland in subsequent days.
OL,15,FDuring the disorder, a leisure centre
OL,16,Fin Larne that had been temporarily
OL,17,Fused to house migrants whose homes had
OL,18,Fbeen targeted in Ballymena, was
OL,19,Fattacked.
