OL,3,CMan charged over arson attack on
OL,4,Cleisure centre during riots
OL,6,FThe centre was extensively damaged in
OL,7,Fthe arson attack and remained closed
OL,8,Ffor several months.
OL,10,FThe PSNI said it had now charged a man
OL,11,Fwith offences related to the incident.
OL,13,FThe 25-year-old is charged with arson,
OL,14,Friotous behaviour and criminal damage.
OL,16,FHe has also been reported to the
OL,17,FPublic Prosecution Service for
OL,18,Fconspiracy to commit arson being
OL,19,Freckless as to endanger life.
