OL,3,CMan charged over arson attack on
OL,4,Cleisure centre during riots
OL,6,FHe is due to appear before Ballymena
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on December 18.
OL,9,FPolice said a 32-year-old man, who was
OL,10,Falso arrested and released on bail in
OL,11,FJune, has been reported to the PPS for
OL,12,Fconspiracy to commit arson being
OL,13,Freckless as to endanger life, riotous
OL,14,Fbehaviour and assisting offenders.
OL,16,FPolice revealed last month they have
OL,17,Fmade 100 arrests since the serious
OL,18,Frioting erupted.
