OL,3,CMan charged over arson attack on
OL,4,Cleisure centre during riots
OL,6,FThe violence began in June after two
OL,7,Fteenage boys, who spoke to a court
OL,8,Fthrough a Romanian interpreter, were
OL,9,Fcharged with the attempted rape of a
OL,10,Fyoung girl in Ballymena.
OL,12,FA peaceful protest in the Co Antrim
OL,13,Ftown was followed by attacks on police
OL,14,Fand properties housing ethnic
OL,15,Fminorities, described by police at the
OL,16,Ftime as "racist thuggery".
