OL,3,CMan charged over arson attack on
OL,4,Cleisure centre during riots
OL,6,FThe disturbances lasted for several
OL,7,Fnights and spread to other areas of
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland including Portadown,
OL,9,FLarne, Belfast, Carrickfergus,
OL,10,FLondonderry and Coleraine.
OL,12,FThe PPS revealed last month that the
OL,13,Fcharges against the two boys were
OL,14,Fbeing withdrawn because of
OL,15,F"significant evidential developments"
OL,16,Fin the case.
